      <title>Rebels seized control of Syrian capital. And, Trump's 1st post-election TV interview</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/12/09/g-s1-37455/up-first-newsletter-syria-bashar-al-assad-donald-trump-tv-interview</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2024/12/09/g-s1-37455/up-first-newsletter-syria-bashar-al-assad-donald-trump-tv-interview</comments>
