      <title>Books We Love is back. Here are some highlights. And, what to expect on Black Friday</title>
      <author>Andrew Limbong</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/11/29/g-s1-36025/books-we-love-black-friday</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2024/11/29/g-s1-36025/books-we-love-black-friday</comments>
