/900/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb2%2F1e%2F0b9d68534521ae898c4fbc73af10%2Fimg-0153-e1732321374896.png 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1179x663+0+146/resize/1200/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb2%2F1e%2F0b9d68534521ae898c4fbc73af10%2Fimg-0153-e1732321374896.png 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1179x663+0+146/resize/1600/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb2%2F1e%2F0b9d68534521ae898c4fbc73af10%2Fimg-0153-e1732321374896.png 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1179x663+0+146/resize/1800/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb2%2F1e%2F0b9d68534521ae898c4fbc73af10%2Fimg-0153-e1732321374896.png 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1179x663+0+146/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb2%2F1e%2F0b9d68534521ae898c4fbc73af10%2Fimg-0153-e1732321374896.png" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/png" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1179x663+0+146/resize/1100/quality/50/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb2%2F1e%2F0b9d68534521ae898c4fbc73af10%2Fimg-0153-e1732321374896.png" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1179x663+0+146/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fb2%2F1e%2F0b9d68534521ae898c4fbc73af10%2Fimg-0153-e1732321374896.png" class="img" alt="Emily Beckman wants all her classmates to be able to make snow angels on snow days." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 Emily Beckman wants all her classmates to be able to make snow angels on snow days.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Jeremy Beckman                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;ol class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Emily Beckman of Colorado has set out to change her school's policy of logging on to school-issued laptops to learn&lt;/strong&gt; when snow falls. The 12-year-old wants to bring back &lt;a href="https://www.cpr.org/2024/11/23/save-the-snow-days-a-young-activist-seeks-to-preserve-tradition/"&gt;snow days&lt;/a&gt; to bring joy to her classmates and beyond. (via &lt;a href="https://www.cpr.org/"&gt;CPR&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A deep-sea exploration company thought it might have solved the mystery of Amelia Earhart's disappearance.&lt;/strong&gt; But the underwater image it released doesn't show the wreckage of her aircraft. Instead, it's of a &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/11/25/nx-s1-5205033/amelia-earhart-plane-rock-formation"&gt;plane-shaped natural rock formation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A former Macy's employee allegedly "made erroneous accounting accrual entries" to&lt;/strong&gt; hide up to &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/11/25/nx-s1-5205097/macys-employee-154-million-delivery-expenses"&gt;$154 million in delivery expenses&lt;/a&gt; for nearly three years, the retailer announced yesterday.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;       &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This newsletter was edited by &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/people/859721331/suzanne-nuyen"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Suzanne Nuyen&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
